prompts.frontCover:
Vibrant comic book style illustration of Lao Lao and Jordan from the photo as cartoon astronauts floating in outer space, dynamic and action-packed. The scene is set against a deep indigo cosmos filled with glowing nebulae, pop-art style planets, and twinkling stars.

Jordan, in a stylized astronaut suit, is laughing and pointing excitedly towards a fantastical rocket ship. The rocket ship is designed to look like a giant, multi-layered birthday cake, complete with dripping frosting thrusters and a single, giant candle at the top acting as an antenna.

Lao Lao, also in a custom astronaut suit, floats beside him with a joyous, surprised expression, one hand raised as if to say "Wow!" They are both weightless, their poses suggesting they are happily adrift. The composition is dynamic, with planets like Saturn (with a ring made of sprinkles) and a cratered moon (that looks like a cookie) scattered in the background. Streaking comets and small "POW!" and "ZAP!" comic book sound effects dot the scene.

In the center of the card, in a beautiful, readable, glowing white cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday Lao Lao!" The artwork is flat 2D, with bold outlines, vivid colors, and halftone dot patterns typical of classic comic books.
